                                <p>Visit a doctor of your choice and ask for a <b>First Certificate of Capacity</b></p>
                            </div>
                            <button class="accordion">Step 2</button>
                            <div class="panel">
                                <p>Fill out a <b>Workers Compensation Claim</b> form available on the Workers page of WorkCover WA. If you have any difficulty while completing the form, speak to your employer or call for assistance over phone number 1300 794 744</p>
                            </div>
                            <button class="accordion">Step 3</button>
