                                    <li>If your claim is <b>pended</b>, you will be needed to provide further imformation</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <br>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">For more detailed information please visit <a href="https://www.workcover.wa.gov.au/">Workcover WA</a></p>
