                            <p style="text-align: left;">If a person is injured and needs some time off from work then they can use this claim in order to obtain their lost income.</p>

                            <p style="text-align: left;"><b>Required Documents</b></p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Certificate of capacity</li>
                                <li>Injured workers claim form</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p style="text-align: left;"><b>Weekly payments will be based on the following criteria,</b></p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Pre-injury average weekly earnings</li>
                                <li>Entitlements to sick-leave</li>
                                <li>Entitlements to annual leave</li>
                                <li>Redundancy payments</li>
                            </ul>
                            <br>
                            <br>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">For more detailed information, please visit <a href="https://www.worksafe.vic.gov.au/">WorkSafe Victoria</a></p>
                        </div>

                        <div id="VIC2" class="tabcontent">
                            <p style="text-align: left;">If a person has a work-related injury or obtained some illness at the workplace then they can use this claim in order to pay off their medical expenses or get in return the amount spent by them only for the approved services.</p>

                            <p style="text-align: left;"><b>Required Documents</b></p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Injured workers claim form</li>
                            </ul>
                            <br>

                            <p style="text-align: left;">For more detailed information, please visit <a href="https://www.worksafe.vic.gov.au/">WorkSafe Victoria</a></p>
                        </div>

                        <div id="VIC3" class="tabcontent">
                            <p style="text-align: left;">If a person is injured and also requires time off from the work then the person can be eligible to get this claim.</p>

                            <p style="text-align: left;">Required Documents</p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Injured workers claim form</li>
                                <li>Certificate of capacity</li>
                            </ul>
                            <br>

                            <p style="text-align: left;">For more detailed information, please visit <a href="https://www.worksafe.vic.gov.au/">WorkSafe Victoria</a></p>
                        </div>

                        <div id="VIC4" class="tabcontent">
                            <button class="accordion">Step 1</button>
                            <div class="panel">
                                <p>Arrange the necessary required documents based on the type of claim you wanted to get</p>
                            </div>

                            <button class="accordion">Step 2</button>
                            <div class="panel">
