                        <div id="NT1" class="tabcontent">
                            <p style="text-align: left;">The eligible workers who can apply for claim are as follows,</p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left">
                                <li>Full-time</li>
                                <li>Part-time</li>
                                <li>Casual</li>
                                <li>Other types</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">Every employer is required to have an <b>insurance policy</b> to cover workers injured during the course of their work.</p>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">For more detailed information, please visit <a href="https://worksafe.nt.gov.au/">NT WorkSafe</a></p>
                        </div>


                        <div id="NT2" class="tabcontent">
                            <p style="text-align: left;"><b>1.Statutory (no-fault) claim:</b> For statutory claims, compensation is paid regardless of who was at fault for causing the injury.</p>

                            <p style="text-align: left;">Payments and benefits received for this claim includes the following:</p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left">
                                <li>Weekly payments as income replacement</li>
                                <li>Lump sums to compensate for permanent impairment</li>
                                <li>Hospital and medical expenses</li>

                            </ul>
                            <br>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">2.Common Law Claim:If your injury is caused because of your employers negligence then you can apply for this claim. Common law claim can only proceed after a statutory claim has been lodged, and then accepted by WorkSafe Northern Territory or the relevant self-insurer.</p>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">Payments and benefits received for this claim includes the following:</p>
                            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                                <li>Economic Loss</li>
                                <li>Pain and Suffering</li>
                                <li>Legal Costs</li>
                                <li>Medical and Hospital Costs</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p style="text-align: left;">For more detailed information, please visit <a href="https://worksafe.nt.gov.au/">NT WorkSafe</a></p>
                        </div>

                        <div id="NT3" class="tabcontent">
