                            <div class="panel">
                                <p>Ask your employer and fill out a claim form or you can download it from NT worksafe website</p>
                            </div>
                            <button class="accordion">Step 3</button>
                            <div class="panel">
                                <p>Give the documents to your employer.Your employer will complete their section of claim form and lodge the claim with their insurer within five working days</p>
                            </div>
                            <button class="accordion">Step 5</button>
                            <div class="panel">
                                <p>The insurer will notify you the outcome of your claim within 10 working days</p>
                            </div>
                            <button class="accordion">Step 6</button>
                            <div class="panel">
                                <ul style="text-align:left; ">
                                    <li> If your claim is <b>accepted</b> you will receive weekly compensation payments and compensation for your medical expenses</li>
